 - Amazing!

32
00:02:19,180 --> 00:02:23,520
Junior Niece, take care of Cinderless for me.

33
00:02:29,580 --> 00:02:34,420
Master, what terrible thing did you do to her back then?

34
00:02:35,980 --> 00:02:39,600
Actually, it wasn't much.

35
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:45,340
I figured that since we were engaged we should be honest with each other,

36
00:02:45,340 --> 00:02:49,220
so I told her that I practiced the Art of Chun.

37
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:51,380
Then she asked me a question.

38
00:02:51,380 --> 00:02:53,720
What was the question?

39
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:59,330
She asked how many wives I have had.

40
00:03:01,820 --> 00:03:05,620
And... what was your answer?

41
00:03:05,620 --> 00:03:08,220
I said three of course.

42
00:03:13,580 --> 00:03:18,540
A gentleman like me will have only one wife in each life. Definitely no more than that.

43
00:03:18,540 --> 00:03:23,180
Then I know why Miss Luo called you a playboy.

44
00:03:23,180 --> 00:03:26,140
One life, one wife.

45
00:03:26,140 --> 00:03:28,000
Well, it doesn't sound like a problem.

46
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,040
- Right? 
 - Right.

47
00:03:36,720 --> 00:03:42,297
So, Martial Uncle Baili, what you're saying is the longer you live, the more women you can love.

48
00:03:42,297 --> 00:03:44,780
No, no, no. Wait... that's not what I meant.

49
00:03:44,780 --> 00:03:47,580
What do you mean, then?

50
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:49,180
I mean...

51
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:51,400
Is...

52
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:53,660
Aren't we talking about Master?

53
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:56,860
- Why are you pointing at me all of a sudden? 
 - Right.

54
00:03:56,860 --> 00:03:59,060
We're talking about me.

55
00:04:00,500 --> 00:04:05,000
What are your real thoughts as a woman?

56
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:09,960
Well, from your point of view, every new identity means a new life.

57
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:13,580
She's the love of your life each time you get married.

58
00:04:13,580 --> 00:04:17,100
But in my opinion, no matter how long you've lived,

59
00:04:17,100 --> 00:04:20,820
if you're still the same person, there's only one life.

60
00:04:20,820 --> 00:04:23,620
I'm the only person who is unique to you.

61
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:28,360
The moment you met me is the moment you knew what love was.

62
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:41,880
Master. What was her response after you said that?

63
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:46,630
After that there was a disapproving look,

64
00:04:46,630 --> 00:04:49,220
but she didn't get mad right away.

65
00:04:49,220 --> 00:04:52,010
She then asked me another question.

66
00:04:52,660 --> 00:04:54,580
 What was it?

67
00:04:55,700 --> 00:04:58,900
- She said...
- I know what she said.

68
00:04:59,540 --> 00:05:04,290
She asked how many wives you would have after marrying her.

69
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:08,740
Exactly. Exactly.

70
00:05:08,740 --> 00:05:13,920
Women all over the world indeed think alike.

71
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:19,360
Hey Grandniece, don't be mad at me because of her.

72
00:05:19,360 --> 00:05:21,820
You can ask your marital uncles here.

73
00:05:21,820 --> 00:05:25,740
If they were in that situation what would they say?

74
00:05:26,900 --> 00:05:28,780
Martial Uncle Baili.

75
00:05:28,780 --> 00:05:30,780
What do you think?

76
00:05:33,300 --> 00:05:35,640
If it were me, I'd say...

77
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:39,460
I haven't thought about my next life,

78
00:05:39,460 --> 00:05:43,820
but in this life, I'll love you with all my heart.

79
00:05:51,260 --> 00:05:54,560
Martial Uncle Sikong, how about you?

80
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,080
Me?

81
00:05:56,080 --> 00:06:01,320
I'd say, before I met you I thought a relationship was something temporary.

82
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:03,480
It ends when you pass away.

83
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:08,520
But after I met you I realized that love can cross the bounds of time.

84
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:13,820
After I met you, I will not love or marry anyone else.

85
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:24,550
Then, decades later, I'd say the same thing to another woman.

86
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:31,640
I've lived over 180 years for nothing.

87
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:35,060
- I should call you Master. 
 - No, no. That's not right.

88
00:06:35,060 --> 00:06:39,600
Master, what did you say in the end?

89
00:06:40,660 --> 00:06:45,040
I had a few drinks and I was tipsy that day.

90
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:47,180
And I told her...

91
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,080
I said...

92
00:06:53,660 --> 00:06:56,600
There's too many to count.

93
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,800
Dengtian Tower.

94
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:11,100
What is that?

95
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:13,760
Dengtian Tower in Xueyue City consists of 16 floors.

96
00:07:13,760 --> 00:07:16,700
Every floor is guarded by a martial master.

97
00:07:16,700 --> 00:07:20,400
The higher the floor, the stronger the martial master.

98
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:22,280
Especially on the top floors.

99
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,600
They're all legends in the Martial World.

100
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:26,180
Their skills are mysterious and powerful.

101
00:07:26,180 --> 00:07:30,240
Only when you pass the top floor will you get a glimpse of Xueyue.

102
00:07:30,240 --> 00:07:31,920
That's impressive.

103
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,920
Indeed.

104
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:36,080
But that's nothing

105
00:07:36,080 --> 00:07:39,940
because I am the legend.

106
00:07:48,250 --> 00:07:50,290

107
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,760
You again?

108
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:07,680
The old City Lord had you stop me, now the current one has too.

109
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:11,500
I also want to ask, why you again?

110
00:08:11,500 --> 00:08:13,360
I haven't seen you in ten years.

111
00:08:13,360 --> 00:08:16,400
Why have you gotten younger?

112
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:20,440
Because... I'm an Immortal.

113
00:08:24,120 --> 00:08:26,600
Master's Iron Head Technique is so powerful.

114
00:08:26,600 --> 00:08:29,120
It never fails.

115
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:47,920
Luo Shui!

116
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:51,840
I'm here.

117
00:08:54,260 --> 00:08:59,080
You once said you preferred a scholar to a warrior.

118
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:01,720
So I took charge of the Academy.

119
00:09:03,140 --> 00:09:08,440
Everyone in this world addresses me as Mister Li from the Academy.

120
00:09:09,300 --> 00:09:11,080
But Mister Li is dead.

121
00:09:11,080 --> 00:09:14,320
In this life, my name is Nangong Chunshui.

122
00:09:14,320 --> 00:09:18,620
In this life, I want to be an elegant scholar.

123
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:25,010
You once asked me a question,

124
00:09:25,010 --> 00:09:29,140
but I answered it incorrectly.

125
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:32,500
But now I'll answer it again.

126
00:09:33,620 --> 00:09:39,310
I, Nangong Chunshui, for this life

127
00:09:40,020 --> 00:09:44,220
and the next lives, have only you as my wife.

128
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:51,190
I used to think that love was temporary.

129
00:09:51,190 --> 00:09:54,500
It ends when one person passes away.

130
00:09:54,500 --> 00:09:56,940
But after I met you

131
00:09:57,510 --> 00:10:03,040
I realized that love can cross the bounds of time.

132
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:11,430
Are you going to say the same thing to another girl after a few decades?

133
00:10:11,430 --> 00:10:13,540
Sikong Changfeng.

134
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,790
You've done this before.

135
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:19,720
I... I was just saying.

136
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:22,180
I didn't expect to get it right.

137
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,390
Of course not!

138
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:34,510
Because... this is my last life.

139
00:10:36,820 --> 00:10:40,820
And I'll spend this life with only you.

140
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:46,560
This life is forever.

